                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-05-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 9, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Milton undoubtedly is a native-born citizen. Laborde says he was born in New
                    Orleans; Gildea, in England. However, one being master and the other mate of an
                    American vessel entitles them to protection of the United States under paragraph
                    171 Consular Regulations, based on statutes, and were, therefore, entitled to be
                    tried under seventh article of the treaty and in accordance with fourth article
                    of the protocol, allowing them to name attorneys and advocates with all other
                    mentioned guarantees, instead of which they have only had a naval officer for
                    their defense. Death sentence asked for by prosecutor not yet imposed, but
                    executions twelve hours afterwards is customary.</p>
            </div>
